Dialogs.Dialog: Manaka
Hey, are you thirsty？
Yeah, I'm feeling a little parched.
Okay, then I'll go buy something to drink. Can you wait me a little？
Sure, of course！
Wait！ I'll do it！
That's the spirit. Wait for me like a good boy. I'm kidding.
I'm sorry to keep you waiting. Here, do you like this one？
Yeah, thank you.
Really？
Of course. I'll be back soon, so wait for me.
Sorry to keep you waiting. Did I took too long？
Welcome back. You didn't have to hurry back, but thank you.
Manaka
Why don't we take a break on that bench？
Sure, sounds good.
Whew. I was getting tired.
I was getting a little tired, so I'll take it easy for a while.
After we rest a little, we should continue our way.
I don't mind staying here like this today...
Forever？
If it's you and me, anywhere, everywhere, forever... I'm kidding.
Of course. Hey, where do you want to go next？
▲高嶺＊＊▲, I'll go anywhere you want to go！
Then, I want to go to your heart▼ I'm kidding.
Manaka
It's a bit hot today. Maybe I should take off my jacket...
Sure, won't that make you feel a little refreshed？
I'm not sure, do you want to get a sunburn？
Really？ I'm so sorry, I didn't know.
Whew. Hmm, now it's so cool.
Haha, you look so comfortable.
Ah... Sure, the sun is a little strong today, isn't it？
Okay, I'll fan you with my hands！
Hehe！ Okay, please▼
Manaka
It's a bit cold today...
Come closer ▲高嶺＊＊▲
Should we move to another place？
I'm feeling a bit cold too, let's warm up▼
...Oh, okay. I understand.
Do you want to go elsewhere？
Hmm... I think it's okay if I stick with you.
I see...
Manaka
Don't you smell something good coming from that shop？
Why don't we go buy something if you're that curious？
Okay, check it out！
We should go together
Welcome back. Was it delicious？
...I bought your share, too. Take it.
Oh, thank you！
I'm curious, so I'll take a look. Wait a minute.
In that case, why don't we go together？
Ah, it was delicious！
That shop seems to be moving around a lot, so we got lucky to come across it, right？
Manaka
Ah, a kitten. I wonder if it'll let me pet it...
Looks a little difficult, why not me instead？
It seems like you can, but...
Huh, do you want me to pat your head？
Yes, just like that！
...Huh！
Ah, hey you've patted me too much！
Hehe！ No running away now♪
I don't know about it, maybe？
Yeah, we should try. Don't scare it, let's go in quiet okay？
It was cute right？ But, I think you're a lot cuter...
Haha, I wonder about that.
Manaka
The sun is strong so strong today... It almost feels like its burning my skin.
You have to apply some sun oil to make your skin prettier！
It's fine to leave as it is！
Huh, is it okay to get a sunburn？
Okay then.
Alright, I think I'll do it. Buy you have to apply it yourself.
...Then do you think I should get a tan？
Well yes, I think.
Alright, I'll do it. But you're going to apply it yourself, okay？
Manaka
Today we have such a beautiful scenery here... Hey, want to take a photo？
I want you to be in the photo with this view, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Okay, let's take our photo together
...I just need you on the photo
Okay, strike a pose！
...Oh, dear.
Oh, that sounds also good. Ask someone to take it for us, please.
Okay, now that that's decided, how about taking it there？
Yes▼ Shall we go？
Manaka
There are a lot of people over there. Is that a popular spot？
I think so, but that makes it somewhat noisy, isn't it？
I think it's lively and that makes it feel nice！
Well, yeah. Just a little bit.
But it's so fun being with you. It's strange how that can be, isn't it？
There are many couples around here, happily looking at the sights. And we are one of those couples.
Hehe！ Are you happy too？
Manaka
There aren't that many people around here... Isn't this a popular date spot？
I think so, but isn't it a bit too quiet？
Don't you feel better with this kind of atmosphere？
It may be better to enjoy the private feeling we have here
I see. Well you're right, we should have fun.
Hehe, yay！
Is it easier to be alone here...？
Well, isn't that something we seek too？
Hehe, oh you. But I think so too... I'm kidding.
Manaka
This rain won't stop...
You're right, this is too much rain... What a shame.
Do you think it's okay if it's rains like this？
Yup...
...It doesn't matter what kind of weather we're in, if I'm with you, right？
...Yeah, you're right, rain may be nice.
Manaka
Can I go to your house on our way back home today？
Of course！
...Sorry！ Maybe next time！
Yay▼ I was somewhat nervous about what I'll do if you said no.
...Why？
...I was kidding. I'm sorry to bother you. Next time, tell me it's okay, please？
Manaka
Do you know there are people who can do fortune telling？ Want to see our compatibility？
Even if you can't see it right away, you can know what the future holds.
Oh, that sounds interesting. Let's go.
...Really？ Hehe♪
...Is it that exciting？
占い師
Your compatibility is the best, and a bright future is ahead of you！
You hear it, a bright future！ How did they know？
That person must be a well-versed future teller.
Hehe. The future, huh...▼
You two are a good match, and your future will go unhindered.
Is it going to go well？
That'll be true even if you didn't predict it！ That's how we are, isn't it？
Yup▼
Your compatibility is... gohogoho！
Well, I certainly didn't get that, did you？
No matter what happens, I'm confident we can get over it！
Me too▼ I'm kidding.
Manaka
Look, over there. Some cute flowers are in full bloom.
Oh, it's true. They are beautiful
But you are a lot cuter, ▲高嶺＊＊▲
I'm sure I wouldn't notice if I was alone
You're right, I would find it difficult too.
We should pay attention to thing like this from now on, shouldn't we？ Just the two of us.
Oh you. Don't say such things with a serious face.
...But that makes me happy. Thank you.
Manaka
Ah！ There's someone from my class over there...
...Do you want to hide from them？
Don't you want them to ask who the person beside you is？
No, it's okay. I want to brag about my date with you.
...I'm kidding though. Why do you think I'll do something like that？ Hehe.
Hmm...？ What's with that？
I see. That only means no one can match the perfect lovers！
Oh you, don't say such things... Even if they're true. I'm kidding▼
Manaka
Hey... What would you do if I suddenly said I don't want to go home today？
What would I do if you'd say that？
You're worried I won't go back？
What！！
...I thought my heart was going to pop out.
Yes, isn't that right？... But, someday...
I really wanna grow up soon...
Manaka
I was getting a little hungry a while ago...
Okay, let's go eat ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Maybe it's just your imagination！
Me？ Well, I'm currently doing some training. Do you know some delicious food nearby？
Oh you, I don't think that's really the case.
Haha, it's okay then.
Manaka
Hey. Is your room clean as usual？
I don't know. Just by having you in it, the air becomes fresh and pink, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
I was thinking you would come, so I cleaned a little before, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Really？ Hehehe！
Then, let's dye it in more Manaka colors, so it lasts for a long time. I'm kidding.
You cleaned it up for me. Thank you.
...But, can you leave it as it is next time？ I'll do it for you, okay？
Manaka
If you were to renovate the room, what would you like me to do first？
Just leave it as it is！
When that time comes, it's better to decide together！
Really？
Of course, that gives it a "▲高嶺＊＊▲ feeling！" to the room, and that's cute.
...I see. Then, you're going to leave it as it is, won't you？
Us, Together... Are we going to think about it？
Of course. I'll help you.
I'm so happy, thank you. When that time comes, please help me▼
Manaka
Ah. Did you brought the sweets for the tea？
I forgot, stay here while I bring them.
It's okay, just wait here a little. I have them here.
...Geez. I can't do anything about it, so I'll give some to you.
Instead, don't go home until I say so, okay？ I'm kidding.
Really？ In that case tell any time you want.
Manaka
...Isn't it funny how we're still not used to being alone together in the same room？
Yeah, it's funny. We like each other a lot
I don't think it's that strange, do you？
I'm so happy. I'm having fun but I'm also excited and anxious.
You too, huh？ Somehow, I felt a bit relieved.
That doesn't mean you dislike that feeling, do you？
I don't know how to explain it...
